WEBVTT

00:03:59.295 --> 00:04:00.487
(Laughter)

00:04:00.511 --> 00:04:03.254
Our help is usually not very helpful.

00:04:03.748 --> 00:04:06.173
Our help is often toxic.

00:04:06.824 --> 00:04:09.620
And help is the sunny side of control.

00:04:10.836 --> 00:04:13.310
Stop helping so much.

00:04:13.334 --> 00:04:16.791
Don't get your help and goodness
all over everybody.

00:04:16.815 --> 00:04:19.327
(Laughter)

00:04:19.351 --> 00:04:21.012
(Applause)

00:04:21.036 --> 00:04:23.009
This brings us to number four:

00:04:23.033 --> 00:04:26.917
everyone is screwed up,
broken, clingy and scared,

00:04:26.941 --> 00:04:29.916
even the people who seem
to have it most together.

00:04:29.940 --> 00:04:32.379
They are much more like you
than you would believe,